s explain data use\non Checkout process is transparent\non Mobile app has appropriate notices\n4.3 Cookie Compliance\non Cookie audit completed\non Cookie policy published\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003ePortability\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eOne month\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eObject\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eImmediate for marketing\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n5.2 DSAR Process\nDSAR Readiness Checklist:\nIntake:\non Request channel established\non Acknowledgment template ready\non Identity verification process\nProcessing:\non Data discovery process documented\non All systems searchable\non Response template created\non Review process established\nDelivery:\non Secure delivery method\non Response format defined\non Tracking system in place\nTimeline:\non One-month deadline tracked\non Extension criteria defined (two further months for complex requests)\non Escalation process established\n5.3 Self-Service Options\non Users can view their data in-app\non Users can update their information\non Users can download their data\non Access management process established\non Employee background checks (where appropriate)\non Security awareness training implemented\non Incident response plan created\non Business continuity plan in place\n6.3 Regular Security Activities\non Quarterly access reviews scheduled\non Annual penetration testing planned\non Regular vulnerability assessments\non Security training refresh schedule\non Security policy reviews scheduled\nPhase 7: Vendor Management\n7.1 Vendor Inventory\non List all vendors processing personal data\non Identify processors vs. controllers\non Document data shared with each\non Assess vendor security posture\n7.2 Data Processing Agreements\n\u003ctable\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003cth\u003eVendor\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth\u003eDPA Status\u003c/th\u003e\u003cth\